:R-HSA-9018676  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0042759 ;
        rdfs:comment        "The D-series resolvins (RvD1-6) are biosynthesised from the precursor ω-3 fatty acid docosahexaenoic acid (DHA), either via aspirin-triggered cylcooxygenase catalysis (17(R) AT-RvDs) or via the lipoxygenase pathway (described here) forming the epimeric 17(S)-RvD1-6 resolvins (Serhan et al. 2014, Bannenberg & Serhan 2010)." ;
        rdfs:label          "Biosynthesis of D-series resolvins" ;
        dc:contributor      "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Edited: Jassal, Bijay, 2017-09-04" , "Authored: Jassal, Bijay, 2017-09-04" , "Reviewed: Hansen, Trond Vidar, 2018-02-21" ;
